message.raw:
SAT Convex vs Convex Face vs Face code works, still not safe though, missing Edge vs Edge and LOTS of space for improvement.
Added libode.la DEPENDENCIES to demo_convex_cd so it gets recompiled when ODE (convex.cpp) is touched.
